    • descending

      @Deprecated public Set<Replacement> descending()
      Deprecated.
      Non-overlapping replacements, sorted in descending order by position. Prefer using ascending() when applying changes, because applying changes in reverse tends to result in quadratic-time copying of the underlying string.
